ISLAMABAD, Jun 22 (APP):Chairman Senate Standing Committee on Information and Broadcasting Senator Faisal Javed has condoled sad demise of religious scholars Mufti Muhammad Naeem and Allama Talib Johri on Monday.
In a condolence message, he prayed the Almighty to rest the departed souls in eternal peace and give enough strength to their families to cope with these huge losses.
